hain-of-thought&#34;&gt;Chain of thought&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#self-consistency&#34;&gt;Self-Consistency&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#general-tips-for-designing-prompts&#34;&gt;General Tips for Designing Prompts&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#common-misconceptions-about-prompts&#34;&gt;Common Misconceptions About Prompts&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#prompt-generator-tools&#34;&gt;Prompt Generator Tools&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#reasoning-model-ie-openai-o1deepseek-r1&#34;&gt;Reasoning Model (i.e. OpenAI o1/DeepSeek R1)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h2&gt;What is prompt engineering?&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;Prompt engineering is about &#34;communicating&#34; with LLM in a way that maximizes the model&#39;s understanding and performance on a given task. At its core, prompt engineering involves designing, refining, and optimizing the text inputs (prompts) given to models to elicit accurate, relevant, and useful responses.&lt;/p&gt;</description><link>https://dannyzheng.me/2025/02/21/prompt-engineering/</link> <pubDate>Mon, 03 Mar 2025 07:08:55 +0000</pubDate><source url="https://dannyzheng.me/feed_rss_created.xml">Danny Zheng</source><guid isPermaLink="true">https://dannyzheng.me/2025/02/21/prompt-engineering/</guid> <enclosure url="https://dannyzheng.me/assets/images/social/2025/02/21/prompt-engineering.png" type="image/png" length="27042" /> </item> <item> <title>Cursor AI Done Right: Lessons from Building Multiple MVPs</title> <author>Danny Zheng</author> <description>Cursor AI Done Right: Lessons from Building Multiple MVPs</description><link>https://dannyzheng.me/2024/10/15/cursor-ai-done-right-lessons-from-building-multiple-mvps/</link> <pubDate>Mon, 03 Mar 2025 07:08:55 +0000</pubDate><source url="https://dannyzheng.me/feed_rss_created.xml">Danny Zheng</source><guid isPermaLink="true">https://dannyzheng.me/2024/10/15/cursor-ai-done-right-lessons-from-building-multipl